this foldable futon sofa, conveniently designed to offer a compact
sleep space without sacrificing comfort. Lower the backrest to
convert this sofa into a padded futon bed in seconds, providing
instant accommodations for last-minute guests. The black
leatherette upholstery, chrome legs and armless frame give the sofa
a sleek, sophisticated finish, while the solid wood construction
